A cozy airport coffee shop interior in Xi'an, China, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures and warm lighting. A circular green mermaid-inspired logo hangs prominently but is deliberately blurred and abstract. Young women in green aprons serve steaming bowls of noodles and dumplings alongside ceramic coffee cups to travelers seated at wooden tables. Through large windows, traditional Chinese architecture mingles with modern airport terminals in the golden afternoon light. Steam rises artfully from dishes, creating a dreamy atmosphere. The scene captures the whimsical fusion of Western café culture meeting Eastern hospitality, with gentle color palettes of jade green, warm wood tones, and soft amber highlights.
